### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "roleId": 1,
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "dni": "12345678",
  "phone": "1234567890"
}

### Verify email (replace with actual code received in email)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "verificationCode": "123456"
}

### Send verification email
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/send-verification?email=test@example.com 